  <h2 class="display-3">About<br /><br /></h2>
  <p class="lead">
Collab is a repository that promotes creative collaboration on a project.<br /><br />

Collab is more visual and interactive than traditional file systems but more organized than traditional digital interactions (email, facebook). Collab follows a comment - leaf - branch idea development structure and broad collaborator access in order to  decentralize collaboration and promote creativity.<br /><br />

What Wikipedia is for facts and historical records, Collab aims to be for more creative topics. We are currently leveraging universal commenting, notifications, integration with youtube, simple and effective layouts using Bootstrap 4, and a comment - leaf branch architecture to provide the most collaborative environment possible.<br /><br />
  </p>

